title: FortiSwitch: CPU Utilization
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/fortinet
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors the CPU utilization of Fortinet FortiSwitch devices via the
 FORTINET-FORTISWITCH-MIB (.1.3.6.1.4.1.12356.106.4.1.2.0).

 The value is an instantaneous sample. Upper WARN/CRIT levels are
 configurable via the "FortiSwitch CPU utilization" ruleset
 (default 80%/90%).

discovery:
 One service is created if the device reports a CPU utilization value.
